regnancy related disability in such an event you can receive up to four months of leave without pay your department cannot refuse to approve your leave without pay if you are unable to return to work within four months you ll be returned to the same position or similar in your department you may request additional disability leave as family leave after four months find out more about voluntary disability insurance vdi adoption assistance stanford's adoption assistance program reimburses you for eligible adoption expenses the program pays up to $10000 per adoption with a maximum lifetime benefit of $20000 per family child care child care financial assistance programs are available for information please refer to these programs dependent day care flexible spending account child care subsidy grant ccsg program for more information on adoption assistance and child care contact the stanford worklife office what to do when you have a child log on to mybenefits within 31 days of the event to add your child to your coverage adjust your life and ad&d insurance or purchase dependent life insurance make changes to your beneficiary designation for life insurance coverage if appropriate start a dependent day care spending account or increase amount of your election quick links see eligibility make changes to mybenefits stanford administrative guide dependent day care flexible spending account child care subsidy grant ccsg program resources how maternity leave works streaming flash presentation 12 14 11 voluntary disability faq maternity faq ca paid family leave insurance brochure family temporary disability benefits faq vdi statement of coverage home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
